      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BUTTER CUP (1) backs up off a brave second at Dubbo on Friday where she drew on the back row and worked but fought on to be beaten 2.5 metres. Came from wider or second row draws in her previous four starts, recording two wins and a second. Should get her chance from the ace draw. ROCKET BOY (4) worked but toughed out a win at Canberra two runs ago and was good again when third at his latest appearance at Wagga. Won the only time he attempted this circuit and distance. Danger. RONZEL SONNY (2) made it two wins from his last three starts when scoring last week at Canberra. Goes well at this distance and a good draw sees him right in contention. Tricky barrier for MAGIC MATTEO (11) but he was impressive in cruising home by 15m at this circuit and distance last start.",
